-of-view
</span>  <span style=3D"color:#930f80;">float</span> focalLength =3D <span =
style=3D"color:blue;">1.0</span> / tan(<span style=3D"color:blue;">0.5</spa=
n> * fieldOfViewY * <span style=3D"color:blue;">3.14159265359</span> / <spa=
n style=3D"color:blue;">180.0</span>);
